reviewText: I recorded this off TV a long time ago, a movie worth watching. She played her part well hunting down a Nazi criminal and what she had to go through doing it. Too bad this film is in French, hopefully this will be released in English in the future.

I don't hate the movie; I hate the fact that I can't watch it because whoever 'owns" this probably wants MORE MONEY to stream it.
How greedy can you get?  Idiots and thieves!  Have a nice day.
